                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, D</hi> 268). I received information, and saw the prisoner and several others in Portman-market. I took Piper there, and told</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="184811270074"></xptr>
               <p>her to look at a lot of eight or ten, and see if she could see the man who stole the scart—she picked out the prisoner—I took him—he said he knew nothing about. it; that I made the girl swear false.</p>
